com.android.dex

Class Mutf8

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.android.dex.Mutf8

  • public final class Mutf8
extends Object
    Modified UTF-8 as described in the dex file format spec.

    Derived from libcore's MUTF-8 encoder at java.nio.charset.ModifiedUtf8.
